            <div type="edition">       
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7214HomilyJCRuf">
                  <label>Homily by John Chrysostom on the archangel Rufāʾel</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Miracles">
                  <label>First collection of miracles of the archangel Rufāʾel</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleImage">
                     <label>On creating a large image of Rufāʾel</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet130"/> according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           <citedRange unit="page">522</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        በእንተ፡ ተአምራቲሁ፡ ወመንክራቲሁ። <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ዘከሠተ፡ ኅቡአቲሁ፡ በትንብልናሁ፡ ለሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል፡ 
                        ወኮነ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ወአዘዘ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ያጸርይዎ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ወርቅ፡ በእሳት፡ እስከ፡ ይትነጠፍ፡ እምርስሕቱ። ወበጊዜሃ፡ ገብሩ፡ ሥዕለ፡ ዓቢየ፡ ዘወርቅ። ንጡፍ፡ 
                        በዓምሳለ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleSeaMonster">
                     <label>Miracle of the keeper of a church, who was carried away by a sea monster</label>
                     <note>This miracle is different from <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7164MRWhale"/>, where a king is swallowed by a sea monster.
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet130"/> according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           <citedRange unit="page">522</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        <choice><sic>አጠይቀክሙ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">አጤይቀክሙ፡</corr></choice> ኦአኃውየ፡ ዕፁበ፡ ወመንክረ፡ 
                        ካልዓ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ተአምረ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ስምዑ፡ እንግርክሙ፡ ኦጉባኤ፡ ማኅበራ፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡
                        ቅድስት፨ ሀሎ፡ ፩ዓቃቤ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወበአሐቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ቦአ፡ ከመ፡ ያብርህ፡ ማኅቶተ፡ ቅድመ፡ <sic>ሥዕል፡</sic> ክቡር፡ ሩፋኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleConstantine">
                     <label>On how Rufāʾel appeared to emperor Constantine</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet130"/> according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           <citedRange unit="page">523</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        ናሁ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ለክሙ፡ ኦአኃውየ፡ ፍቁራን፡ ኃይለ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሩፋኤል፡ አመ፡ ተፈነወ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ቈስጠንጢኖስ፡
                        ንጉሥ፡ ዘተመስሎ፡ ለአብርሃም፡ በሠዊዓ፡ ወልዱ፡ ወምንተ፡ ገብረ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መልአክ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ ወሶበ፡ ረከቦ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>ንዑሠ፡ 
                        መዋዕል፡ ወልዱ፡ ለቈስጠንጢኖስ፡
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="MiracleTobias">
                     <label>Miracle of Tobias</label>
                     <note>
                        The following incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet130"/> according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           <citedRange unit="page">523</citedRange></bibl>.
                     </note>
                     <ab>
                        ሣልስኒ፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለዝንቱ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> መልአክ፡ ነበረ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ በዘመነ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቀደምት። 
                        <choice><sic>ዘልሙ</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ዘስሙ፡</corr></choice> ጦቢት፡ ወስመ፡ ወልዱ፡ ጦብያ። ወሠናይ፡ ውእቱ፡ 
                        ብእሲሁ፡ ወያፈቅሮ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፨ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ወበእንተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ ምስለ፡ ዜና፡ 
                        መልአክ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ነገሩ፡ ለጦቢት፡ ወልደ፡ ጦብያ፤ ወልደ፡ ገባል፡ ዘእምነ፡ አሳሔል፤ ዘእምነገደ፡ ንፍታሌም፤ 
                     </ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT2387Taamme">
                  <label>Second collection of miracles of the archangel Rufāʾel</label>
                  <note>This collection also has an independent circulation (see <ref type="mss" corresp="ANLcr3"/>).</note>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7161MRWomb">
                  <label>Miracle of the power of St Raphael to loosen the womb</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7162MRTheophilus">
                  <label>Miracle of the Patriarch Theophilus who remained buried for three days</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7163MRKidnapping">
                  <label>Miracle of the boy kidnapped by an elephant</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7164MRWhale">
                  <label>Miracle of the king swallowed by a whale</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7165MRThief">
                  <label>Miracle of the thief who had broken into a church that contained treasures</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7166MRDeacon">
                  <label>Miracle of the deacon thrown into the sea</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7167MRHealing">
                  <label>Miracle of the healing powers of St Raphael</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7168MRWidow">
                  <label>Miracle of the poor widow</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7169MRChurch">
                  <label>Miracle of the construction of the church of Rufāʾel in Amḥarā</label>
                  <note>This miracle is different from <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7215HistoryRuf"/>.</note>
               </div> 
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7215HistoryRuf">
                  <label>History of the consecration of the church of Rufāʾel on an island near Alexandria</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT7216HistoryJCRuf">
                  <label>History of how John Chrysostom visited the church of Rufāʾel on an island</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LIT6633SalRufMastafessehe">
                  <label>Salām-hymn to the archangel Raphael</label>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
